# Research Directory

This directory contains structured literature research artifacts.

See `.claude/skills/deep-research/SKILL.md` for the skill documentation.

## Structure

- `questions/` - Research question files (the organizational "hub")
- `sources/` - Source metadata files, organized by question
- `digests/` - Compaction-resistant summaries, organized by question
- `transcripts/` - Full PDF transcriptions when available
